## Failure Modes

| Dependency | Failure | Behavior |
|------------|---------|----------|
| PostgreSQL | Unavailable | Fail-closed; requests return 500 |
| RabbitMQ | Unavailable | Events not published; DB writes succeed (fail-open) |

